getLimitString(String, int, int, String) - 类 中的方法com.jeesite.common.persistence.dialect.db.SQLServer2005Dialect
Add a LIMIT clause to the given SQL SELECT

The LIMIT SQL will look like:

WITH query AS (SELECT TOP 100 percent ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY CURRENT_TIMESTAMP) as __row_number__, * from table_name) SELECT * FROM query WHERE __row_number__ BETWEEN :offset and :lastRows ORDER BY __row_number__
